ZH: 他生气了，把手机扔在了地上。
EN: He got angry and threw his phone on the ground.

ZH: 她把不要的玩具扔进了垃圾桶。
EN: She threw unwanted toys into the trash can.

ZH: 孩子们玩得太开心，不小心扔掉了书包。
EN: The children were playing too happily and accidentally threw away their backpacks.

ZH: 他把心情不好的信扔进了火炉里。
EN: He threw the letter with a bad mood into the fireplace.

ZH: 她生气地把衣服扔进了洗衣机。
EN: She angrily threw the clothes into the washing machine.

ZH: 你不能在公共场所随便扔垃圾。
EN: You can't just throw garbage around in public places.

ZH: 妈妈看到地上有垃圾，生气地指着儿子说：“谁扔的？”
EN: Mom saw garbage on the floor and angrily pointed at her son, asking: "Who threw this?"

ZH: 在野外旅行时，要注意不要扔垃圾。
EN: When traveling in the wilderness, be careful not to litter.

ZH: 她把不要的东西扔掉，让房间变得整洁。
EN: She threw away unwanted items, making the room tidy.

ZH: 他生气地把键盘扔在地上。
EN: He angrily threw the keyboard on the ground.

ZH: 孩子把沙子扔进了湖里。
EN: The child threw sand into the lake.

ZH: 她扔掉了那封让她伤心的信。
EN: She threw away the letter that made her sad.

ZH: 这个城市已经取缔了随地扔烟蒂的行为。
EN: This city has banned the act of throwing cigarette butts on the ground.

ZH: 我不喜欢别人在街上随地扔垃圾。
EN: I don't like it when people throw garbage on the streets.

ZH: 他开车扔掉了一个空罐子。
EN: He tossed an empty can out of the car.

ZH: 她扔掉了过期的食物。
EN: She threw away expired food.

ZH: 他不小心把饼干盒扔到了地上。
EN: He accidentally threw the cookie box on the ground.

ZH: 大家一起来捡拾垃圾，不要随便扔。
EN: Let's pick up litter together and not throw it around.

ZH: 小孩子玩得开心，把玩具扔到了远处。
EN: The children were playing happily and threw their toys far away.
